tiles

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • tiles.Tile

  • public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
    Tile represents each individual cell of the Map. It holds the different layers, such as ground and resources. It also holds its north, south, east, and west as a node.
    Author:
    Gateway
